ActPesticide Residue Compensation Act
SubjectRegistrar of appeals ** APPOINTMENT **
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 1982-3443 of November 18, 1982; and (2) appointing the person from time to time holding the office of Chief Administrator of the Courts Administration Service to be REGISTRAR OF APPEALS to carry out the purposes of Part II of the Pesticide Residue Compensation Act.
